Confirmation Step - Add Client Flow

## Page Structure
- Title: "Add Client" with icon
- Stepper showing 5 steps (all complete except step 5 "Confirmation" which is current/in progress)
- Action buttons: "Confirm" (primary), "Save as Draft" (secondary), "Go Back" (tertiary)

## Info Banner
- Type: Info notification
- Title: "Review and Confirm Details"
- Body: "You cannot edit information on this screen. To make changes, click the edit icon next to the section you want to update."
- Background: #E5F8FB (Feedback/Info Tint)
- Border: 1px #002677 (Optum/Secondary/Dark Blue)
- Border radius: 12px

## Accordion Sections (Collapsible Review Panels)

### 1. Client Details Accordion
- Header: "Client Details" with edit icon
- Subtitle: "Please review all fields you have filled out and make sure they are correct before clicking on confirm."
- Expandable with chevron
- Contains read-only display of:
  - Client Reference ID*, Client ID (disabled), Client Name*
  - Client Status (dropdown), Source* (dropdown)
  - Multiple Address sections (Address Type*, Address 1*, Address 2*, City*, State*, Zip*)
  - "Add another address" button

### 2. Contract Details Accordion
- Header: "Contract Details" with edit icon
- Subtitle: "Please review all fields you have filled out and make sure they are correct before clicking on confirm."
- Collapsed by default

### 3. Contacts & Access Accordion
- Header: "Contacts & Access" with edit icon
- Subtitle: "Complete the fields below."
- Collapsed by default

### 4. Operational Units Accordions (Multiple)
- Header: "Operational Units - Operational Unit Name" with edit icon
- Subtitle: "Please review all fields you have filled out and make sure they are correct before clicking on confirm."
- Multiple instances shown (3 in design)
- Collapsed by default

## Styling
- Accordion container: white background, 1px #CBCCCD border, 12px border radius
- Section title: Desktop/Heading/XXS (20px, bold, #000000)
- Section subtitle: Desktop/Body/L/Regular (16px, #4B4D4F)
- Edit icon: 24x24px, positioned next to title
- Chevron: 12x7.84px for expand/collapse

## Stepper States
- Steps 1-4: Complete (checkmark icon)
- Step 5: Current/In Progress (numbered circle with shadow effect)
